Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它正在远方伺机而动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一边是具备棘手火力的黑魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一边是已经中了一击的负伤猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,两边分开行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它肯定是会选我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然也是因为我刻意设计
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让魔物不会靠近托基希可了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,总之是成功遇敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就得一路逃过他的攻击\N直到到达避难所了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是在肚子开了个洞的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,《不道德公会》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:33.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1610,1080)\fad(200,550)\3c&HC32CB0&}完全燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,和闪避蛛战斗最棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,既不是剧毒与丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是力量与感知等能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而是摸不清它能力的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是资讯量过少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的闪避蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是以狩猎小型魔物为主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,30公分左右的的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,某方面算是益虫般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不会被大多数护卫看作是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因此不足的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只能靠反复试误来填补
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然而就这家伙来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一发生失误
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再也无法进行下次尝试的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,实在过于巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只能祈祷没有更多新情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再被刺上一次肯定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙不只是对于\N直接针对身体的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对于像是以火焰包围这种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,间接的敌意也会产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然乍看之下是个毫无死角的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但这两部分可以推测出共通点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,视线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不论哪种都需要满足\N看着它这个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我现在正以\N将它诱入陷阱这个目的逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但它却没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然时而对其释放杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但它也没有回避的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不看着它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,赏它一击恐怕也是做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的力量并不足以在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不进行瞄准的情况下决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况要是无谓地刺激它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让它产生警戒彻底逃跑\N才是最糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要攻击那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,必须第一击就给它致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还挺有跑酷天分的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,托基希可你一看到我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就闭上眼睛准备发动高级咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我有设置驱魔装置 所以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只要待在这里面就不会被魔物袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那要是想去厕所该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就地解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,知道不能上厕所之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,反而会格外敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,本来我的名字就已经够危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要是失禁的话可不是闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老板 可以快点回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快做个了结啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为失血过多开始意识朦胧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,装作被逼入绝境的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,开始多了几分真实感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一道工序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再躲开一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不能盯着它看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如此一来回避的关键就在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,影子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,930)\fad(300,0)\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}30分钟前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爆燃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,非常简单的解释就是指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在火灾现场引发的爆炸现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,又是烤肉又是烧房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的魔法到底是用来做什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,烤肉是你自己的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个方法虽然无法造成致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但却能产生\N令它无法应对敌意的空档
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能压制它麻烦的移动能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是现在 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然后去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爆焰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,托基希可 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,除了衣服以外都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样该怎么回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有上衣可以借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你可不可以穿衣服时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便打电话求救…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,托基希可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也因为疲劳跟耗尽魔力都铁腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要倒在我身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在我能走路以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就先维持这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你都不会害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这部分就算是福利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟老板今天一个人这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记我在憋尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就让小便付之流水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我同时在做学院和公会的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但我仍然需要向学校提交活动报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他们对待学生的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 西塔姆困在蜘蛛网上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当我试着帮她时 我也被缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当你试图逃脱时 网会更加缠绕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它们已经离得如此之近了……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,每当它们的皮肤相互摩擦时 一股电流会穿过身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,无限循环 它们不停地相互刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服都被烧焦了 为了逃脱 只好忽略尴尬感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,火越烧越旺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,经历了无数次高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,作者？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,《不道德公会》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:42.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1570,1080)\fad(200,550)\3c&H0096FF&}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,疲劳还是没有消除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为闪避蛛受到的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就算已经解毒了 但伤口仍然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天在那种状态下太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,闻闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,依心 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 想说阿基昨天非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天一定很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就来照顾你的生活起居
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是一样美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让你特地来一趟真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我才刚起床还没吃任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的依心只能做到这些事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,光是会做料理就很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要是来的是其他三个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我就会再次陷入沉睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…伤势还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 昨天有让梅蒂娜治疗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,乱来造成的疲劳还在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但伤口已经连痕迹都不留了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说是危及性命的重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来托基很在意战功的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她觉得把讨伐闪避蛛的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,归给她这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟给予最后一击的是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,况且我又打算辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要是现在不小心得到好评价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就更难走人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,功劳不过是个重担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,功劳是重担啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,待…待会可以一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,街上买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,150)\frz352.8\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H6565C8&}成长茁壮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,420)\frz352.8\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说是买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么想买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐的食材之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐也请交给依心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小依心 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,蔬菜店老板你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小依心是来买晚餐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,待会也来看看我们家肉铺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,依心 谢谢你上次分给我炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这熟门熟路的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最近才搬来萌芽镇的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 马上就要一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天进了很好的苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就送你一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,免费附送吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这座城镇十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都没和居民聊过天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如何啊小依心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然季节还有点早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但这颗粒很分明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不只可以用在料理上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的用途也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,蔬菜屋老板的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别的用途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这种状况是可以退货的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便也受到性骚扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 依心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有被这群人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么奇怪的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有的时候讲的话有点难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们都是温柔的好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小依心应该用再小一号的运动裤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来雕塑一下大腿的赘肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,又更圆了一圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好想用我的肉来养她的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要品尝看看我的特制蛋蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面都能感受到的变态感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基也…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要试着打好关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天特别强势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,作为礼貌还是该问候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来和小依心很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小依心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别说是打好关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌隙还更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下 阿基是这座城镇的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是很照顾依心的厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 还以为是个带着不纯眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看着小依心的变态家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城镇的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不会出现在杂志或电视上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得你的样子真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,给你 小依心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 老兄你也拿些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你每次都为了城镇努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 依心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也给那边的哥哥一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是依心经常\N提到的那个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着依心走到哪里都被送了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也被感谢讨伐的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 现在就开始期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,回礼的料理该做些什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是单纯收下好处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪你会这么有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉可以做很多供品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,供品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,依心每天都会去参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,附近的狐狸大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,依心姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是双胞胎们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐姐 来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我偶尔会陪附近的小孩玩英雄游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,依心演的是反派女干部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来做不出什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,女干部 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 没有受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不痛 一点都不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那小鬼 该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以摸 这种色色的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"色色"是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我很纯真所以什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会从纯真的人口中\N听到的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,总…总之把手从胸部移开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 跳绳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,女干部 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,正义必胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,手段有够邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是依心输了 我投…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,依心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都说投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我国对造反者绝不手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的生杀大权掌握在我们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,平常…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"这种事"是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事"是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.02,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,320)\fad(100,0)\3c&H0096FF&\c&H12FBF3&}无邪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.02,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500,320)\fad(100,0)\3c&H0096FF&\c&H12FBF3&}无邪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在时机不对的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,时机凑巧地装纯真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,使不出…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那里…不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原酿我啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说这已经算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\3c&HB6CBFF&\c&H6565C8&\move(350,1080,330,942.5,2,669)}颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:42.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(330,943)\fad(0,300)\3c&HB6CBFF&\c&H6565C8&}颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:43.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HC32CB0&\c&HF4EAF8&\fad(0,200)\move(1400,1080,1502.5,897.5,3,1212)}喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的魔物时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不肯放手这点比魔物还要残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然想对小鬼说的话一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也别输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,初次相遇时那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都还不是会做这种事的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么让那些孩子们学坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,八成是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到你以前都还很普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那肯定是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,果然对品德教育有不良影响
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,话说我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要带我来街上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的你有点奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想让阿基…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让阿基知道自己在守护些什么事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我在守护的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基想要辞去护卫的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,依心不想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也不愿意去阻止这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…至少希望是能带着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,愉快的心情辞去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,镇上大家的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都是靠阿基守护的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望阿基能够以\N这些美好的事为傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要是拼上性命努力以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最后却留下了讨人厌的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就太令人难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今天第一次被镇上的人\N说了"谢谢你"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们并没有特别轻视护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我都不去和他人对话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己没有主动接触他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还对于自己独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感到不公平而散发不满
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱持着只要换个环境\N就会有回报的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还让依心替我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阿基
